SELECT a.attname
  FROM (
         SELECT indrelid, indkey, generate_subscripts(indkey, 1) idx
           FROM pg_index
          WHERE indrelid = '"featured_tags"'::regclass
            AND indisprimary
       ) i
  JOIN pg_attribute a
    ON a.attrelid = i.indrelid
   AND a.attnum = i.indkey[i.idx]
 ORDER BY i.idx

SELECT "tags".* FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "statuses_tags" ON "statuses_tags"."tag_id" = "tags"."id" INNER JOIN "statuses" ON "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = "statuses_tags"."status_id" WHERE "statuses"."id" IN (SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."account_id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $2) AND "tags"."id" NOT IN (SELECT "featured_tags"."id" FROM "featured_tags" WHERE "featured_tags"."account_id" = $3) GROUP BY "tags"."id" ORDER BY count(*) desc LIMIT $4
